functions.tag:
{
  pages:
  [
    "[{\"text\":\"It's been several months since I passed the gates of this village and have been accepted by its residents. As an explorer from distant places I wouldn't have thought to find civilizations beyond the great sea, yet here I am in a lush forest with all kind\"}]",
    "[{\"text\":\"of exotic trees and animals the people back home wouldn't believe. At first when we arrived at the shores of this new land I wouldn't have imagined such a village would exist in these forests as simply being here would require all sort of materials\"}]",
    "[{\"text\":\"to survive. These people, however, have very simple solutions to the problems caused by the environment. They also seem to live in harmony with their surroundings, using it to their advantage rather than fighting it. It's truly admirable,\"}]",
    "[{\"text\":\"making me think we have much to learn should we ever create a grand settlement here.\"}]"
  ],
  title:"Tai Bwo Bwarg - A Simple Village",
  author:"Emor, the Explorer",
  display:{Lore:["An Explorer's Note"]}
}

{
  pages:
  [
    "[{\"text\":\"Under these mighty trees there's a whole other world to discover. Big chasms with possibly huge treasures. I and a group of explorers have made friendly contact with the tribesman of this village and set out to explore this new world until we found floating\"}]",
    "[{\"text\":\"islands with a rather interesting combination of resources underneath. While digging we found out there's a huge world buried underneath. Today marks the day we will set out and explore these massive caverns. I wonder what secrets they hide...\"}]"
  ],
  title:"Under the Mighty Trees",
  author:"Unknown",
  display:{Lore:["A note of exploration."]}
}
